Class DummyI18nManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.tools.i18n.impl.DummyI18nManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    I18nManager

    public class DummyI18nManager
extends Object
implements I18nManager
    Dummy I18nManager implementation to be used when there has not been registered an implementation. Returns as value the same message to get the translation for.
